query:
SELECT c.id, c.concertDate, c.createdAt, a.name as artistName, v.name as venueName 
FROM concerts c 
JOIN artists a ON c.artistId = a.id 
JOIN venues v ON c.venueId = v.id 
WHERE a.name LIKE '%Speed%' 
LIMIT 5;
